{"tid":1451101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T18:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:37:44.000Z","uid":57465,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c9085dd2103bb663a6a13b4be48897aafeda4189","tid":1451101,"uid":57465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:21:12.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=c7bef5e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=1c8518a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"c83e3767dfb0f417812fb2f447b3fea54778fd55","tid":1451101,"uid":291937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:24:33.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"166ffc403409304908ea58eebcb15ec028629da1","tid":1451101,"uid":219767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:25:48.000Z","msg":"咁撚鍾意射頭"},{"pid":"3cd19d93c9d640dbdc2f37bce4faad13c582e3ff","tid":1451101,"uid":283109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">機場文宣整合post</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1450351\" data-auto-link target=\"